2. Frontend shell — Eigent
   Author:  Eigent AI (eigent-ai)
   Source:  https://github.com/eigent-ai/eigent
   License: Apache License 2.0 (see frontend/LICENSE)
   Use:     The desktop/web frontend shell (Vite + React + Tailwind UI kit,
