            product surfaces were replaced with the Verdict VC analysis UI.
            Apache-2.0 source license headers are retained in modified files.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. Research reference — SSFF (Startup Success Forecasting Framework)
   Paper:   "Startup Success Forecasting Framework" (arXiv:2405.19456)
   Authors: Xisen Wang et al.
   Source:  https://github.com/xisen-w/Startup-Success-Forecasting-Framework
   Use:     The multi-agent analyst design (founder/market/product analysis,
            founder L1–L5 segmentation, chief integration) is inspired by
            SSFF. Verdict deliberately keeps only the LLM-analyst pipeline and
            drops SSFF's ML components (random forest, neural-net idea-fit,
            embeddings). See the README "Design notes" for the rationale.
